{"tid":1524913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日拆閘 各做各","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T20:51:11.000Z","uid":258214,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d374b6921bea945c371b2c85e6daefb4b70cdfb4","tid":1524913,"uid":258214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日如果見到有人拆閘<br />\n唔該一係幫手拆<br />\n一係幫手擔遮<br />\n一係幫手睇水<br />\n一係就當睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n你唔支持都好，咪撚阻住曬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n攜帶噴漆遮擋CCTV更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刮花廣告板、爆玻璃等自由發揮。<br />\n<br />\n入機場前順手拆閘，<br />\n首選機場沿線，其他自由發揮。<br />\n但記住機場先係主線，拆黨鐵為支線任務<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n聽日901機場見"},{"pid":"2f0f113ab919e9e34e2fe23703289939f5c2c337","tid":1524913,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">全民跳閘運動</span></strong><br />\n香港人，可以應承我嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk8A4uB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk8A4uB.png&h=ad5893d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77c546512ddd1424a4d0ff812c24fe7b79f98754","tid":1524913,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=7bd6c4cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=12d69161\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=e5d67ca4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"2d51a434891cc8057b6d9bc1923cb7374b5c69a8","tid":1524913,"uid":134781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:25.000Z","msg":"9月1 變咗全民拆黨鐵 送頭行動<br />\n各有各做？ 送完頭再去機場！ 正呀<br />\n點解呢排港鐵加裝cctv? 肯定係巧合啦<br />\n<br />\n推緊拆黨鐵post 既你入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好去機場 繼續去各區 等更多義士比人拉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3b183e10b5e4897b894cc61d017643666546fc4","tid":1524913,"uid":275172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:40.000Z","msg":"拆完，一係罷搭<br />\n一係瘋狂坐免費地鐵"},{"pid":"5b45c31101bedd656a76a8f6ecd8b03d613c1993","tid":1524913,"uid":72626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce29c98c5eacdfe7db9c242ada571a425d391d6e","tid":1524913,"uid":258214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b183e10b5e4897b894cc61d017643666546fc4","tid":1524913,"uid":275172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:40.000Z","msg":"拆完，一係罷搭<br />\n一係瘋狂坐免費地鐵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"只要佢唔停，老閪都坐免費鐵"},{"pid":"c2e0fef8bb2e69617e4224f81c22975714791514","tid":1524913,"uid":258214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"28c881107664de1269f8d5039ffbb834e6a2a8e3","tid":1524913,"uid":93540,"lik